text: The Elusive Avengers () is a 1966 Soviet adventure movie directed by Edmond Keosayan.Тигран Кеосаян пришел в гости к Корчевникову с двумя женамиНеуловимые мстители It stars Viktor Kosykh, Valentina Kurdyukova, and Vasily Vasilyev. ==Actors== * Viktor Kosykh – Danka Shchus * Valentina Kurdyukova – Ksanka Shchus * Vasily Vasilyev – Yashka the Gypsy * Mikhail Metyolkin – Valerka Meshcheryakov * Yefim Kopelyan – chieftain Ignat Burnash == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1966 adventure movies Category:Soviet adventure movies Category:Movies directed by Edmond Keosayan
title: The Elusive Avengers
